CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 3, 1956, pg. A12 reads: "Babies In Contest - These winsome tots competed for honors in Wilberforce baby contest which was held last Friday in the Centre Avenue YWCA building. Left to right, they are Patricia Ann Rivers, DeWayne Green, winner of third prize; Michael Moore, winner of first prize; Thomas Anthony Jr., winner of second prize, and Laura Ann Jackson...Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of baby contestants, from left: Patricia Ann Rivers, DeWayne Green, Michael Moore, Thomas Anthony Jr., and Laura Ann Jackson, posed on striped sofa with wooden legs in Centre Avenue YWCA
